            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De adulatione: blandimento et assentione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/>De adulatione / blandimento et 
              <lb ed="#P" n="28"/>assentione capitulum quartum:-
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/><ref>Salomon in prouerbiis. ca. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e127">Si te iacta
               <lb ed="#P" n="30"/>verint peccatores non aquiescas eis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e133">
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="31"/><ref>Ibidem xxvi. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e135">meliora sunt vulnera 
               <lb ed="#P" n="32"/>diligentis quam fraudientis oscula blan
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="33"/>dictis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#P" n="34"/><ref>Isocrates in exhortationibus. ca. .</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e148">Odi blan
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="35"/>dientes tanquam decipientes / nam utrique 
               <lb ed="#P" n="36"/>commissarii facti iniuriantur commissis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#P" n="37"/><ref>Aristoteles rethoricorum libro. primo. ca. xx.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="38"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e160">adulationem recipere et adulari detes
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="39"/>tabile est. apparens abicus adula
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="40"/>tor est.</quote> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="41"/><ref>Idem libro. ii. ca. ix.</ref> <quote>laudare presentem
               <lb ed="#P" n="42"/>adultationis est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e172">
               <lb ed="#P" n="43"/><ref>Idem ethincorum libro iiii. ca. iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e174">omnes
               <lb ed="#P" n="44"/>blanditores obsequiosi seruiles / et humiles
               <lb ed="#P" n="45"/>sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#P" n="46"/><ref>Ibidem libro. viii. ca. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e184">amatores adu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="47"/>lationis multi sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e190">
               <lb ed="#P" n="48"/><ref>Idem magnorum moralium. libro. ca.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="49"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e192">adulator est plus decentibus / et 
               <lb ed="#P" n="50"/>existentibus adiciens.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#P" n="51"/><ref>Terentius in andria. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e204">hoc tempore obse
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="52"/>quium amicos <sic>vedtatas</sic> odium parit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e211">
               <lb ed="#P" n="53"/><ref>Tullius rethoricorum artis noue libro
               <lb ed="#P" n="54"/>v. ca. vi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e215">habet assentatio iocunda princi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="55"/>pia / eadem exitus amarissimos affert.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e223">
               <lb ed="#P" n="56"/><ref>Ouidius sine titulo sine amoris libro. primo.
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/>ca. viii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e227">Impia sub dulci melle venena 
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/>latent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#P" n="59"/><ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. libro. vi. epistola
               <lb ed="#P" n="60"/>iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e237">adulatio que similis est amicitie 
               <lb ed="#P" n="61"/>nomiatur tium illa sed vincit et preterit
               <lb ed="#P" n="62"/>aptis ac propitiis auribus recipitur ac in precor
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="63"/>dia ima descendit et ipso gratiosa 
               <pb ed="#P" n="48-r"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="1"/>quo ledit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e254">
               <lb ed="#P" n="2"/><ref>Idem in prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e256">habet suum venenum blanda 
               <lb ed="#P" n="3"/>oratio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e262">
               <lb ed="#P" n="4"/><ref>Auctor libri de formula honeste vite. 
               <lb ed="#P" n="5"/>ca. iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e266">adulatores de vita. difficilli
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="6"/>mum continentie opus est assentationes 
               <lb ed="#P" n="7"/>adulantium repellere quorum sermones
               <lb ed="#P" n="8"/>animum quadam voluptate resoluunt 
               <lb ed="#P" n="9"/>per assentatione amicitiam merearis hanc 
               <lb ed="#P" n="10"/>promerendi a te aditum aliis pandas
               <lb ed="#P" n="11"/>non acerba sed blanda timebis. Cun
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="12"/>ctis esto benignus nemini blandus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e287">
               <lb ed="#P" n="13"/><ref>Cato ca. ii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="14"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e291">Noli homines blando nimium sermone pro
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="15"/>bare fistula dulce canit volu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="16"/>crem dum decipit auceps.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e300">
               <lb ed="#P" n="17"/><ref>Idem. ca. iiii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="18"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e302">Sermones blandos blesosque vitare memento
               <lb ed="#P" n="19"/>Simplicitas veri fraus esse fama ficta 
               <lb ed="#P" n="20"/>loquendi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e310">
               <lb ed="#P" n="21"/><ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum libro. xii. et fi: epistola
               <lb ed="#P" n="22"/>x.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e314">grauius percutit / qui blandiendo 
               <lb ed="#P" n="23"/>crassatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e320">
               <lb ed="#P" n="24"/><ref>Idem de anima.<!--This is badly smudged - looks like a mistake--> ca. xxvi. et ante pe.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="25"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e322">hostis dulcis amicus amarus est</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e330">
               <lb ed="#P" n="26"/><ref>Versificator fabularum exopi. lxiiii. fa
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="27"/>bula / et fi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e334">Blanditie plus quam vene
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="28"/>na / nocent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e340">
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/><ref>Montenarius in luna cleri. ca. xxviii.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P" n="30"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e344">Sugit adulator lac pectoris ad uber.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-d1e350">
               <lb ed="#P" n="31"/><ref>Prouerbium vulghare /</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d24815-Qd1e354">losenge del
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="32"/>nimico e come / passare alponico:</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
